(1187, 166, 'sub-page-content', 'Cox Digital Solutions and Cox Cross Media have merged to form our new company appropriately called Gamut. Gamut was formed to offer publishers and advertisers a full spectrum of support and comprehensive media solutions.\r\n\r\nWe offer a broad spectrum of smart media from programmatic to direct. Gamut provides comprehensive media solutions that optimize ad revenue for publishers and create access to key audiences for advertisers. We deliver cross-channel television and digital campaigns that build on our long history of media excellence and benefit from the most advanced data-driven tools. Whether locally, regionally or nationally, Gamut connects publishers and buyers for optimum results. Gamut is a wholly owned subsidiary of Cox Media Group.\r\n\r\nContact us to learn more.'),
