(2719, 217, 'additional_info', 'Michael Scott is senior vice president, strategic partnerships, for Gamut, where he leads all revenue initiatives for Gamut’s four business units. \r\n\r\nA longtime industry veteran, Scott has a proven track-record of spearheading business development (Do we have a tangible example to cite, i.e. increased sales 250% at XYZ company?). \r\n\r\nOver the course of his professional career, Scott has held leadership roles in the television, marketing services, marketing data and sports marketing industries. He was an integral member of the leadership team that built the Olympics and sports marketing team for NBC TV stations. Scott is also the founder of X, a customer content creative agency, where he worked with brands like X to help X.\r\n\r\nScott received a degree in advertising from the University of Florida.'),
(2720, 217, '_additional_info', 'field_5419deabd7bca'),
