(2725, 218, 'additional_info', 'Rachel Allgood is senior vice president of marketing and consumer insights for Gamut. In this role, she oversees all marketing efforts for Gamut’s robust suite of capabilities, driving sales growth through innovative marketing solutions. \r\n\r\nAllgood is a marketing veteran with 25 years’ experience. She has directed the planning, design and execution of hundreds of integrated marketing campaigns – including interactive, print, packaging, brand identity, and public relations – for a range of brands spanning Fortune 500 companies to startups. She joined Gamut from Cablevision, where she served as X and was responsible for the productization of set-top box data as Total Audience Data ® Portfolios. Prior to that, Allgood launched and managed two branding, communication and advertising solutions firms. \r\n\r\nAllgood graduated from X. '),
