(2777, 225, 'additional_info', 'Mary Barnas serves as vice president for Gamut. In this role, Barnas leads the Cross Media+ team, which offers full media planning, buying, execution, and reporting in a streamlined service for multi-market and cross-platform campaigns. Barnas is also responsible for overseeing media strategy and full backroom support for agencies and small to mid-sized businesses.\r\n\r\nBarnas has more than 25 years’ experience in agency roles, and almost two decades serving in top leadership positions focused on local media. Her expertise is in media planning and buying, and has worked on a wide range of projects in the past (do we have past examples to site?). \r\n\r\nBarnas was the recipient of Adweek’s Media All Start award in 2008. She began her career at X. She is a graduate of College of Mt. St. Vincent. '),
