(2783, 223, 'additional_info', 'Laura Stinnett is vice president of national sales at Gamut. In this capacity, she oversees Reps+, which provides hands-on sales consultation for site-specific executions, powered by deep-rooted local expertise and access to high quality data to achieve national campaign goals. \r\n\r\nStinnett brings more than 15 years’ experience in digital media advertising to Gamut. Over the course of her career, she has successfully led revenue-driven sales teams with a focus on strategic and innovative client solutions. Previously, Stinnett served as vice president of sales at News Distribution Network (NDN), where she helped build out the sales and business development teams as well as grow revenue. Stinnett also served as director of sales at Brightroll, and spent a decade at Cox in Atlanta working in various management roles for Cox Interactive Media and The Atlanta Journal Constitution, where she was responsible for digital sales both locally and nationally.\r\n\r\nStinnett is an International Advertising Bureau certified digital media sales executive. She graduated from East Tennessee State University with a degree in mass communications.'),
(2784, 223, '_additional_info', 'field_5419deabd7bca'),
