(3175, 221, 'additional_info', 'Lisandro Lejano is Gamut’s vice president of product management. In this role, Lisandro is responsible for the definition and execution of Gamut’s long-term product vision. \r\n\r\nLisandro has extensive experience launching online advertising products. Previously, he served as the product lead, building TeleNav’s proprietary mobile ad serving platform. Lisandro began his career at Yahoo! where he managed a suite of internal sales and order management tools, culminating in the deployment of Yahoo’s current order management platform, APT.\r\n\r\nLisandro graduated from Cal Poly, San Luis Obispo with a degree in business administration.                                                                         '),
