(4718, 349, 'sub-page-content', 'Gamut offers a broad spectrum of smart media from <a title="Programmatic+" href="http://gamut.dev/?page_id=11">programmatic</a> to direct, providing comprehensive media solutions that optimize ad revenue for publishers and create access to key audiences for advertisers.\r\n\r\nGamut is comprised of four channels that offer a full-spectrum of smart media solutions. So, whether our customers are buying or selling inventory, they can feel certain that their dollars are producing maximum value programmatically, directly, or through a network.'),
