(4731, 350, 'main-first-p', 'The answer to a question we are asked almost every day: “Does programmatic replace humans?”'),
(4732, 350, '_main-first-p', 'field_54172dc9d0281'),
(4733, 350, 'main-p', '<a title="Programmatic+" href="http://gamut.dev/?page_id=11">Technology</a> does replace some tasks as there are certain things machines do better, however, there are some things that humans do better. We know the difference. Programmatic allows us to apply marketing strategy at scale.\r\n\r\nAutomation does not mean technology is a substitute for a quality customer experience. At Gamut, we employ Smart Service to make our technology work hardest for you.\r\nGamut’s Programmatic solution differentiates itself by going the extra mile with: exclusive and high quality inventory, cutting-edge yield optimization, and ease of adoption through our zero-commitment TestDrive technology.\r\n\r\nOur technology optimizes across the inventory value spectrum — display, video, and mobile — so each party can be confident that their dollars and/or inventory are producing maximum value.\r\n\r\nWe can help optimize your assets for maximum value.'),
(4734, 350, '_main-p', 'field_54172debd0282'),
