(4898, 355, 'three-column-content_1_column-content', 'The CrossMedia+ team aligns the campaign to your KPIs.\r\nWe reveal insights during each campaign to optimize for the best performance. Self-service and full-service reporting is available daily, weekly, and at specific campaign milestones.'),
