(5368, 383, 'sub-page-content', '<p class="first-p-text">Smart Service makes our technology work hardest for you.  It’s advanced technology PLUS human understanding.</p>\r\nWhat we’re talking about is Service. Real, human, committed-to-your-goals service that stream-lines the media selling and buying process. Gamut is comprised of four solution groups to effectively offer a full-spectrum of media solutions. So, whether our customers are buying or selling inventory, they can feel certain that their dollars are producing maximum value programmatically, directly, or through a network.\r\n\r\nYes, you read right, Smart Service rules even when selling and buying programmatically. With private exchanges, “try-before-you-buy-it” testing, easy-to-use dashboards, and yield optimization — at Gamut, automation does not mean technology is a substitute for a quality customer experience. Instead, it frees us up to do what we do best — continue to make media even smarter.\r\n\r\nContact us to learn more.'),
